{"tid":1697970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六成人拒收貨 施政報告僅30.8分","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:05:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a32f33f8a0e82526b6aa7e168204ffd4353d5447","tid":1697970,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191107/XJN5OP6UCK2JA67PHG7INB2QH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191107%2FXJN5OP6UCK2JA67PHG7INB2QH4%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=6c60fb4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191107%2FXJN5OP6UCK2JA67PHG7INB2QH4%2F&h=ab92f903\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191107/XJN5OP6UCK2JA67PHG7INB2QH4/</a><br />\n<br />\n六成人拒收貨 施政報告僅30.8分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191107/large/1573056769_cb55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573056769_cb55.jpg&h=4827b545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭上月推出新一份《施政報告》，無助緩和社會衝突。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【中大民調】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中大亞太研究所上月底就《施政報告》進行電話訪問調查，57.8%受訪者不滿意今年的《報告》，對今年《報告》的平均評分為30.8分，為及格水平之下，亦比去年暴跌了22分。<br />\n<br />\n這份《施政報告》是林鄭月娥在反送中抗爭爆發後，被視為挽回民望的重點武器。中大亞太研究所於10月22日至28日以電話訪問714名18歲或以上的市民，57.8%受訪者不滿意《報告》，比去年的同一調查不滿度增加29個百分點。<br />\n無助解決社會衝突<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：屯門拉票遇襲 電光火石制服藍衣人<br />\n<br />\n而表示滿意的只有11%，較去年急降24.8個百分點。調查又要求受訪者為《報告》評分，受訪者認為今年的《報告》平均評分為30.8分，屬不及格，比去年調查跌了22分。<br />\n<br />\n至於《報告》主打的房屋議題，6.2%受訪者認為房屋問題，與近日香港民怨的關聯很小或完全沒有關聯， 86.4%受訪者認為《報告》對解決當前社會衝突的幫助效果很小，只有1.4%則認為很大幫助。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"9cad3ba683258c2b62766699058419893bc48bc8","tid":1697970,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2edb60e1c06605c8479aed68f27f92867177eae9","tid":1697970,"uid":82553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"仲有30.8分咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bab7fcd96996f9462a9800449aa252be0818e18","tid":1697970,"uid":149879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"係咪點撚錯小數點"}]}